
ent-RMCWeaponPistolNP92 = NP92 pistol
  .desc = The standard issue sidearm of the SPP. The NP92 is a small but powerful sidearm, well-liked by most it is issued to, although some prefer the weapon it was meant to replace, the Type 73. Takes 12 round magazines.
ent-RMCWeaponPistolNPZ92 = NPZ92 pistol
  .desc = The NPZ92 is a version of the NP92 that includes an integrated suppressor, issued sparingly to Kommando units.
